meta.name: memcached
meta.description: Dashboard for the telegraf input plug-in: Memcached
meta.author: influxdata

queries.query: SELECT max("curr_connections") AS "current_connections" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: count

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("get_hits")) AS "get_hits" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: hits/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("get_misses")) AS "get_misses" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: misses/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("delete_hits")) AS "delete_hits" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: deletes/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("delete_misses")) AS "delete_misses" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: delete misses/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("incr_hits")) AS "incr_hits" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: incr hits/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("incr_misses")) AS "incr_misses" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: incr misses/s

queries.query: SELECT max("curr_items") AS "current_items" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: count

queries.query: SELECT max("total_items") AS "total_items" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: count

queries.query: SELECT max("bytes") AS "bytes" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: bytes

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("bytes_read")) AS "bytes_read" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: bytes/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("bytes_written")) AS "bytes_written" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: bytes/s

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(max("evictions"), 10s) AS "evictions" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."memcached" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND "host"=:host: GROUP BY time(:interval:)
queries.label: evictions / 10s
